channel.title: Anybody know any good decompilers?
channel.description:
Title says it all; I wanna dissassemble the client that MoparScape uses and see if theres some way I can upgrade it for a server with better graphics. I also need to figure out the main_file_cache.dat thing, apparently it stores all the information for the game thats needed for the sever.
Basically, I need a tool to take apart MoparScape at a fundamental level and put it back together in a way I please.
Reward: Adminship on the new server/game? How the hell should I know. Depends on the quality of the decompiler. If it works count on a rep point at the least.
